00:32:50.620 --> 00:32:51.909
Jimbo.

00:32:58.767 --> 00:33:00.001
Come here.

00:33:16.428 --> 00:33:18.647
Enjoying it, huh?

00:33:19.141 --> 00:33:20.840
It’s good, right?

00:33:21.378 --> 00:33:23.761
Eat and help me think, Jimbo.

00:33:24.794 --> 00:33:25.830
What should I do?

00:33:29.523 --> 00:33:31.937
I’ll be right back.

00:33:43.594 --> 00:33:44.598
Uncle.

00:33:50.234 --> 00:33:51.339
Praew is pregnant.

00:33:57.130 --> 00:33:59.130
Leng must take responsibility.

00:34:00.348 --> 00:34:02.348
We must get married in my hometown.

00:34:02.348 --> 00:34:04.512
My parents won’t allow us to live like this.

00:34:06.793 --> 00:34:08.092
Calm down, Praew.

00:34:08.777 --> 00:34:10.640
It’s not like I’m running away.

00:34:11.226 --> 00:34:13.500
You do realize that both of my parents passed away, right?

00:34:13.500 --> 00:34:15.039
Where should I get the money from?

00:34:15.935 --> 00:34:17.612
You should give me time to make the money.

00:34:17.612 --> 00:34:19.363
But my growing tummy can’t wait, Leng.

00:34:19.882 --> 00:34:21.882
Praew, easy.

00:34:22.921 --> 00:34:24.456
Figure it out together.

00:34:24.456 --> 00:34:25.950
Leng isn’t going anywhere.

00:34:35.751 --> 00:34:36.673
Uncle,

00:34:37.001 --> 00:34:39.283
should I borrow the money from Madam Jintana?

00:34:40.700 --> 00:34:42.344
Can you even handle the interest?

00:34:42.493 --> 00:34:43.928
It’s 10%.

00:35:02.866 --> 00:35:04.346
You say you don’t have money.

00:35:04.346 --> 00:35:05.757
But you always do for cigarettes, huh?

00:35:06.789 --> 00:35:08.789
It’s just 4 baht a piece.

00:35:09.266 --> 00:35:10.580
I’m stressed out.

00:35:10.580 --> 00:35:11.852
I just want to feel better.

00:35:11.852 --> 00:35:13.037
You’re not the only one with stress.

00:35:13.037 --> 00:35:13.892
I can’t spend 4 baht or what?

00:35:13.892 --> 00:35:14.712
No!

00:35:14.712 --> 00:35:15.528
Hey!

00:35:15.692 --> 00:35:17.117
Don’t fight.

00:35:18.362 --> 00:35:20.499
We can’t find the way out right here right now.

00:35:20.742 --> 00:35:22.742
Who else knows about this, Praew?

00:35:22.742 --> 00:35:23.705
Your parents?

00:35:35.713 --> 00:35:36.731
What are you doing here, Uncle Jim?

00:35:37.713 --> 00:35:38.804
Shopping.

00:35:39.027 --> 00:35:40.671
Almost done here. I’m headed home.

00:35:41.154 --> 00:35:41.970
Uncle Jim,

00:35:43.830 --> 00:35:44.877
want to grab something to eat?

00:36:15.995 --> 00:36:17.995
[Kongsup Insurance]

